#: ../../R/Real-Soon-Now.rst:5
msgid "Real Soon Now"
msgstr "Real Soon Now"

#: ../../R/Real-Soon-Now.rst:7
msgid "adv\\."
msgstr "副詞"

#: ../../R/Real-Soon-Now.rst:9
msgid ""
"[orig. from SF's fanzine community, popularized by Jerry Pournelle's column "
"in *BYTE*\\]"
msgstr "[元はSFのファンジンコミュニティから。Jerry PournelleのBYTE誌(\\ *BYTE*\\)のコラムによって広まった]"

#: ../../R/Real-Soon-Now.rst:13
msgid ""
"Supposed to be available (or fixed, or cheap, or whatever) real soon now "
"according to somebody, but the speaker is quite skeptical."
msgstr "誰かによれば本当にもうすぐ利用可能になる(あるいは修正される、安くなる、その他何であれ)はずだが、話し手はかなり懐疑的である、という意。"

#: ../../R/Real-Soon-Now.rst:16
msgid ""
"When one's gods, fates, or other time commitments permit one to get to it "
"(in other words, don't hold your breath). Often abbreviated RSN. Compare "
":ref:`copious-free-time`\\."
msgstr ""
"自分の神々、運命、その他の時間的責務がそれに取りかかることを許したとき(言い換えれば、期待しないで待て)。しばしばRSNと略される。\\ "
":ref:`copious-free-time`\\ と比較せよ。"
